verbose_text: Similarly, when the expression of the myogenic factor MyoD1 was evaluated to measure the treatment effect of the 3 different doses of miR-206, significant differences were observed between the 15-mug and 30-mug but not between the 30-mug and 60-mug miR-206 doses (XREF_FIG; XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
